<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOURTH OF JULY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Today is Independence Day, the 213th anniversary of the adoption of the 
Declaration of Independence. 
</P>
<P>
Closed: All government offices, courts, banks, post offices, stock and 
commodity exchanges, libraries and many businesses. RTD buses will follow 
Sunday schedules. 
</P>
