STUDENTS; HUMAN RIGHTS -- CHINA; FREEDOM; CHINA -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT 
REGULATION; POLITICAL ACTIVISM; CHINESE -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
