above Rose Hills Cemetery in Puente Hills, near Whittier. EUGENE TANNER / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, With shovels and axes, firefighters move in to prepare 
fire breaks. ; Map, Fire Area, FRANK BURSINGER / Los Angeles Times 
