came upon the scene of the Puente Hills fire accomplished a daring rescue of a 
firefighter who had been trapped on the burning roof of a home at 14418 Cabinda 
Drive. The civilian was identified as Jose Cruz of West Covina. The firefighter 
was not named. STEVE DYKES / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
