<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST: CAPISTRANO BEACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Goodwill site: Goodwill Industries has arranged for a donation station at 
Palisades United Methodist Church, 27002 Camino de Estrella. The station is 
open from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. seven days a week and is staffed by an attendant who 
can issue receipts for donations. Pickup of items too large to be taken to the 
station can be arranged by calling (714) 547-6300. Donations of reusable 
household goods support Goodwill's job-training and rehabilitation programs for 
physically and mentally disabled people. 
</P>
</TEXT>
