Joyner's third-inning double as catcher Jim Sundberg awaits throw. ; Photo, 
Angel left-hander Jim Abbott struck out six, walked one and retired 13 of the 
last 15 batters to earn his seventh victory. DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times 
