<TEXT>
<P>
Robert Furtado has been named to the newly created position of vice president 
of operations for Ingram Micro D. He had been director of operations for Micro 
D Inc. since July, 1987. Micro D merged earlier this year with Ingram 
Industries Inc. to form Ingram Micro D. Ingram Micro D, with headquarters in 
Santa Ana, is a wholesale distributor of microcomputer products. 
